# @param {String} num1
# @param {String} num2
# @param {Integer} min_sum
# @param {Integer} max_sum
# @return {Integer}
def count(num1, num2, min_sum, max_sum)
  mod = 10**9 + 7

  def digit_sum_dp(dp, num, max_sum)
    n = num.size
    sum = 0
    count = 0

    (0...n).each do |i|
      digit = num[i].to_i

      (0...digit).each do |d|
        (0..max_sum).each do |s|
          count += dp[n-i-1][s] if s + d <= max_sum
        end
      end

      sum += digit
      break if sum > max_sum
    end

    count += 1 if sum <= max_sum && sum >= 0
    count
  end

  def prepare_dp(max_len, max_sum)
    dp = Array.new(max_len+1) { Array.new(max_sum+1, 0) }
    dp[0][0] = 1

    (1..max_len).each do |i|
      (0..max_sum).each do |j|
        (0..9).each do |d|
          dp[i][j] += dp[i-1][j-d] if j-d >= 0
        end
      end
    end

    dp
  end

  max_len = [num1.size, num2.size].max
  dp = prepare_dp(max_len, max_sum)

  count2 = digit_sum_dp(dp, num2, max_sum)
  count1 = digit_sum_dp(dp, (num1.to_i - 1).to_s, max_sum)

  (count2 - count1) % mod
end
